== Check every action of every controller

* User creation - with invite / without invite
* forgotten password
* enumerate airframes in index
* Images import and upload

== Usability scenarios

* create aircraft with listing images
* upload a spec file
* send a spec file to a friend
* track recipient activity
* update spec file
* send updated spec file to all leads

== misc

* check all error pages, make sure they work
* make sure error page images/assets are correct

== AUTO TESTING

run `spork` in a console to start DRB server to make iterative testing really quick
use `rspec --drb specs` to execute specs (ie, `rspec --drb specs/models` for just models)
use Faker to come up with random names (http://rubydoc.info/github/stympy/faker/master/frames)